title: Flight Simulator 2020   MSFS Update   Local legends and famous flyer receive update
description:
In this video we will have a look at the updates which have been released a few hours ago for the following aircrafts:

- Local Legend 14: Bell 47J Ranger
- Local Legend 6: Junkers F 13
- Famous Flyer 7: Mitsubishi Heavy Industries MU-2

The Bell 47J is the winner when counting the number of updates followed by the Junker F13. The Mitsubishi only received one fix related to an issue with the external view.
